{
  "id": "generate_voronoi_polygons@1",
  "version": "1.0",
  "env_id": "gvsig_desktop_env@0.1",
  "description": "Generate Voronoi (Thiessen) polygons from the populated places layer (/home/ga/gvsig_data/cities/ne_110m_populated_places.shp). Save the output shapefile to /home/ga/gvsig_data/exports/voronoi_cities.shp and ensure the resulting layer is added to the View.",
